    "68206880": {
      "title": "Girdlestone pseudarthrosis for a failed total hip arthroplasty",
      "abstract": "A well-timed pseudarthrosis may still be the only acceptable outcome for a failed total hip arthroplasty. That comparatively little has been written on the subject is probably a reflection of the fact that few surgeons have treated sufficient numbers or have the enthusiasm to be an authority on a subject which, after all, is regarded as the ultimate failure of total hip arthroplasty."
